passages.name: houseInformationManual
passages.text:
<Message>
  {EMBARK_MOVING_SE_HOUSE_INFORMATION_MANUAL_MESSAGE_1}
</Message>

<GroupedResponse>
  <Title>
    {EMBARK_MOVING_SE_HOUSE_INFORMATION_RESPONSE_TITLE}
  </Title>
  <Item>
    {EMBARK_MOVING_SE_HOUSE_LIVING_SPACE_LABEL}: {livingSpace} {EMBARK_MOVING_SE_APARTMENT_SQUARE_METERS}
  </Item>
  <Item>
    {EMBARK_MOVING_SE_HOUSE_ANCILLARY_AREA_LABEL}: {ancillaryArea} {EMBARK_MOVING_SE_APARTMENT_SQUARE_METERS}
  </Item>
  <Item>
    {EMBARK_MOVING_SE_HOUSE_CONSTRUCTION_YEAR_LABEL}: {yearOfConstruction}
  </Item>
</GroupedResponse>

<NumberActionSet next="[[{EMBARK_MOVING_SE_CONTINUE_BUTTON}->houseBathrooms]]">

                placeholder="120"
                minvalue="1"
                key="livingSpace"
                unit="{EMBARK_MOVING_SE_APARTMENT_SQUARE_METERS}"
  >
    <Tooltip>
      <Title>
        {EMBARK_MOVING_SE_HOUSE_LIVING_SPACE_LABEL}
      </Title>
      <Description>
        {EMBARK_MOVING_SE_HOUSE_INFORMATION_LIVING_SPACE_DESCRIPTION}
      </Description>
    </Tooltip>
  </NumberAction>
  <NumberAction title="{EMBARK_MOVING_SE_HOUSE_ANCILLARY_AREA_LABEL}"
                placeholder="60"
                key="ancillaryArea"
                unit="{EMBARK_MOVING_SE_APARTMENT_SQUARE_METERS}"
  >
    <Tooltip>
      <Title>
        {EMBARK_MOVING_SE_HOUSE_ANCILLARY_AREA_LABEL}
      </Title>
      <Description>
        {EMBARK_MOVING_SE_HOUSE_INFORMATION_ANCILLARY_AREA_DESCRIPTION}
      </Description>
    </Tooltip>
  </NumberAction>
  <NumberAction title="{EMBARK_MOVING_SE_HOUSE_CONSTRUCTION_YEAR_LABEL}"
                placeholder="1998"
                minvalue="1"
                key="yearOfConstruction"
  >
    <Tooltip>
      <Title>
        {EMBARK_MOVING_SE_HOUSE_CONSTRUCTION_YEAR_LABEL}
      </Title>
      <Description>
        {EMBARK_MOVING_SE_HOUSE_INFORMATION_CONTRUCTION_YEAR_DESCRIPTION}
      </Description>
    </Tooltip>
  </NumberAction>
</NumberActionSet>

passages.name: houseAddress
passages.text:
<Message>
  {EMBARK_MOVING_SE_HOUSE_ADDRESS_MESSAGE_1}
</Message>

<TextActionSet next="[[{EMBARK_MOVING_SE_CONTINUE_BUTTON}->houseInformation]]">
  <TextAction title="{EMBARK_MOVING_SE_APARTMENT_ADDRESS_ADDRESS_FIELD}"
              placeholder="{EMBARK_MOVING_SE_APARTMENT_ADDRESS_ADDRESS_PLACEHOLDER}"
              large="true"
              key="streetAddress"
  >
  </TextAction>
  <TextAction title="{EMBARK_MOVING_SE_APARTMENT_ADDRESS_POSTAL_CODE_FIELD}"
              placeholder="{EMBARK_MOVING_SE_APARTMENT_ADDRESS_POSTAL_CODE_PLACEHOLDER}"
              mask="PostalCode"
              key="postalNumber"
  >
  </TextAction>
  <HouseInformationApi match="[[houseInformation]]"
                       nomatch="[[houseInformationManual]]"
                       error="[[houseInformationManual]]"
  >
  </HouseInformationApi>
</TextActionSet>

passages.name: CreateQuoteError
passages.text:
<Message>
  Something appears to have gone wrong and we can’t give you a price quote right now. Try again, and if it doesn’t work you can write us in the chat on the website!
</Message>

passages.name: apartmentPeople
passages.text:
<Message>
  {EMBARK_MOVING_SE_APARTMENT_PEOPLE_MESSAGE_1}
</Message>

<Redirect when="livingSpace > 250"

passages.name: houseExtraBuildings
passages.text:
<Message>
  {EMBARK_MOVING_SE_HOUSE_EXTRA_BUILDINGS_MESSAGE_1}
</Message>

<Message>
  {EMBARK_MOVING_SE_HOUSE_EXTRA_BUILDINGS_MESSAGE_2}
</Message>

<GroupedResponse>
  <Title>
    {EMBARK_MOVING_SE_HOUSE_EXTRA_BUILDINGS_RESPONSE_TITLE}
  </Title>
  <Each key="extraBuildings">
    {type.Label}, {area} {EMBARK_MOVING_SE_APARTMENT_SQUARE_METERS}
  </Each>
</GroupedResponse>

<MultiAction maxamount="4"
             key="extraBuildings"
             next="[[{EMBARK_MOVING_SE_CONTINUE_BUTTON}->accessDate]]"
>
  <Add label="{EMBARK_MOVING_SE_ADD_BUILDING_BUTTON}">
    <DropdownAction key="type"
                    label="{EMBARK_MOVING_SE_DROPDOWN_PLACEHOLDER}"
    >
      <Option value="GARAGE">
        {EMBARK_MOVING_SE_EXTRA_BUILDING_GARAGE}
      </Option>
      <Option value="ATTEFALL">
        {EMBARK_MOVING_SE_EXTRA_BUILDING_ATTEFALL}
      </Option>
      <Option value="FRIGGEBOD">
        Friggebod
      </Option>
      <Option value="GUESTHOUSE">
        {EMBARK_MOVING_SE_EXTRA_BUILDING_GUESTHOUSE}
      </Option>
      <Option value="CARPORT">
        {EMBARK_MOVING_SE_EXTRA_BUILDING_CARPORT}
      </Option>
      <Option value="SAUNA">
        {EMBARK_MOVING_SE_EXTRA_BUILDING_SAUNA}
      </Option>
      <Option value="BOATHOUSE">
        {EMBARK_MOVING_SE_EXTRA_BUILDING_BOATHOUSE}
      </Option>
      <Option value="OTHER">
        {EMBARK_MOVING_SE_EXTRA_BUILDING_OTHER}
      </Option>
    </DropdownAction>
    <NumberAction placeholder="20"
                  key="area"
                  unit="{EMBARK_MOVING_SE_APARTMENT_SQUARE_METERS}"
    >
    </NumberAction>
    <SwitchAction key="hasWaterConnected"
                  label="Water connected"
                  defaultvalue="false"
    >
    </SwitchAction>
  </Add>
</MultiAction>

          when="personalNumber.Age >= 30 || livingSpace > 50 || householdSize > 2"

passages.name: Offer
passages.text:
<GraphQLApi next="[[OfferSuccess]]">
  <Mutation>
    mutation CreateAddressChangeQuotes(
  $contractBundleId: ID!
  $type: AddressHomeType!
  $street: String!
  $zip: String!
  $livingSpace: Int!
  $numberCoInsured:Int!
  $ownership: AddressOwnership!
  $startDate: LocalDate!
  $isStudent: Boolean
  $ancillaryArea: Int
  $yearOfConstruction: Int
  $numberOfBathrooms: Int
  $isSubleted: Boolean
  $extraBuildings: [AddressHouseExtraBuilding!]
) {
  	createAddressChangeQuotes(
		input: {
			contractBundleId: $contractBundleId
      		type: $type
      		street: $street
      		zip: $zip
      		livingSpace: $livingSpace
     		numberCoInsured: $numberCoInsured
      		ownership: $ownership
      		startDate: $startDate
      		isYouth: false
  			isStudent: $isStudent
  			ancillaryArea: $ancillaryArea
			yearOfConstruction: $yearOfConstruction
			numberOfBathrooms: $numberOfBathrooms
			isSubleted: $isSubleted
  			extraBuildings: $extraBuildings
		}
	) {
	  ... on AddressChangeQuoteSuccess {
      	quoteIds
      }
   	  ... on AddressChangeQuoteFailure {
      	breachedUnderwritingGuidelines
      }
	}
}
  </Mutation>
  <Variable key="contractBundleId"
            from="contractBundleId"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="type"
            from="homeType"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="street"
            from="streetAddress"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="zip"
            from="postalNumber"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="livingSpace"
            from="livingSpace"
            as="int"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="numberCoInsured"
            from="householdSize"
            as="int"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="ownerShip"
            from="apartmentType"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="startDate"
            from="movingDate"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="isStudent"
            from="isStudent"
            as="boolean"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="ancillaryArea"
            from="ancillaryArea"
            as="int"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="yearOfConstruction"
            from="yearOfConstruction"
            as="int"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="numberOfBathrooms"
            from="numberOfBathrooms"
            as="int"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="isSubleted"
            from="isSubleted"
            as="boolean"
  >
  </Variable>
  <MultiActionVariable key="extraBuildings"
                       from="extraBuildings"
  >
    <Variable key="type"
              from="type"
              as="string"
    >
    </Variable>
    <Variable key="area"
              from="area"
              as="int"
    >
    </Variable>
    <Variable key="hasWaterConnected"
              from="hasWaterConnected"
              as="boolean"
    >
    </Variable>
  </MultiActionVariable>
  <Result>
    key="createAddressChangeQuotes.quoteIds"
		as="quoteIds"
  </Result>
  <Result>
    key="createAddressChangeQuotes.breachedUnderwritingGuidelines"
		as="breachedUnderwritingGuidelines"
  </Result>
  <Error next="[[CreateQuoteError]]">
  </Error>
</GraphQLApi>

<Message>
  OK! Your offer is ready!
</Message>
